metadata.title: Jenkins the Degen
metadata.name: Jenkins the Degen
metadata.description: Jake the Degen and Jenkins the Valet have come together for a free-to-claim collaborative collection exclusive to their communities. The collection contains 3 pieces, each a unique interpretation of Jenkins the Valet by Jake. The art titles and rarities are as follows: Jenkins the Degen (75%), Peep Show (20%), Love Feedback (5%).
